textBox.richText: Before copying links over from the old RMR OtherLinks page, I tested the link to make sure it was still active before entering it on the OffsiteLinks TWiki page. It seems on the original page, I had Aqsis as www.aqsis.com instead of www.aqsis.org. Sor when I tested the .com link, no aqsis. So I incorrectly concluded that they weren’t around any more. That mistake has been corrected. Started to move some of the Converter links over to the OffsiteLinks TWiki.
